{"tid":1827462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張超雄質疑民政專員離場違中立　羅智光指事件推得太遠","createTime":"2020-01-17T03:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T03:36:55.000Z","uid":226984,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5b99155b1c6f6e37c553dfbb250ba67c518c4662","tid":1827462,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:23:59.000Z","msg":"立法會財委會繼續審議公務員加薪撥款申請。民主黨尹兆堅說，基於目前的警方濫暴問題，要求將警隊分拆處理。<br />\n<br />\n昨日在中西區區議會上，當議員動議有關譴責警務處處長鄧炳強時，民政事務專員指不能認同未必是事實的內容，因此與其他政府人員離席。工黨張超雄說，公務員需保持政治中立，但當政府立場與區議會民意代表不同，在席公務員決定離場是要與民為敵，他質疑如果政府官員日後在立法會上與議員立場相反，是否也可以拂袖而去。<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局局長羅智光回應時，重申審議加薪項目時不會將警隊分拆出公務員團隊。他說，政府不同意昨日區議會的做法，又指不論公務員個人的政治立場，都要對特首及政府完全忠誠，如果有相違的話，藉不同方式表達意見都是理所當然，認為大家將昨日的事推得太遠。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503298-20200117.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503298-20200117.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyhSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=8cb1e88a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1503298-20200117.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3679736e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1503298-20200117.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"bb52327bdfdbcf2a2ef65786733c53bf26b1d236","tid":1827462,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9c5886490459bc642fab86ed2c2de65813cf5d","tid":1827462,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:28:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"467e490179036bb859e23694ba32fe02e1596c85","tid":1827462,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:28:48.000Z","msg":"拉闊d?"},{"pid":"02e756d15bc69c7f5ecaaedd11b9b606357adefd","tid":1827462,"uid":39796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:30:46.000Z","msg":"樓上幾正<br />\n<br />\n不過警犬都要死全家"},{"pid":"e371177029e513da2fa46e68a5239ac70b7821f3","tid":1827462,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:31:39.000Z","msg":"（重開）如何利用文宣滲入藍色經濟圈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1827330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1827330</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8dc3a71e8567648045c0ea2b79615c25af381224","tid":1827462,"uid":129348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02e756d15bc69c7f5ecaaedd11b9b606357adefd","tid":1827462,"uid":39796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:30:46.000Z","msg":"樓上幾正<br />\n<br />\n不過警犬都要死全家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:36:55.000Z","msg":"五毛黎，佢想啲po比人bam曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}